title: Como Upper Level Duplex, Laundry, Off Street Parking, Avail Now
posting_body: ['Upper Level Como Duplex, Laundry, Parking, Hardwood Floors, Video Walk Through', 'Property Address', '1026 15th Ave SE | Minneapolis, MN 55414', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'This unit is available for in person showings.', 'Video walk through and photos are located on the Guardian Property Management website.', 'This home will be available for an 8-1 through 9-1 move in.', 'Walking into the unit you will find a large living room and dining with hardwood floors.', 'The bathroom is very large and kitchen has a dining nook.', 'Upstairs you will find the 3rd bedroom, office/storage room.', 'Parking is available in back and shared with the lower unit.', 'Pets are welcome with positive rental reference and credit score.', '(Dog deposit $500, Cat $200)', 'Lawn and snow are taken care of by the owners.', 'You are responsible for gas and electric.', 'Pets are welcome with positive rental reference and credit.', '(Dog fee $30mo, Cat fee $20mo)', 'Applications are available on the Guardian Property Management website.', 'Each application is $50 per adult and can be paid with a credit or debit card.', 'Application is based on income, credit history (Guardian Property Management will not use credit score but will be using information from your credit report), rental/work history and includes a criminal background check.', 'For full criteria visit our website and click “apply now” on the listed unit.', 'Any additional questions please call or email Billy.', 'Broker: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Agent:', 'Billy Sommers', 'Amenities', 'Off-Street Parking', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,400', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,650.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,650.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
